title: The Lamp of Psyche by Edith Wharton

content.question: In a well-written essay, analyze how Wharton uses literary elements and techniques to convey Delia’s complex character.

frqParts.text: In a well-written essay, analyze how Wharton uses literary elements and techniques to convey Delia’s complex character.

skill.text: Skill 1.E: Explain how a character's own choices, actions, and speech reveal complexities in that character, and explain the function of those complexities.
